CHARISMA

Your charisma ^Wattribute^n represents how attractive you are to other people.
Attractiveness though is not necessarily physical beauty.  Charisma allows
you to be more persuasive (getting those better prices), helps you relate
better to the people you meet, and helps all sorts of negotiations.  If you
are a ^Wmage^n or ^Wshaman^n, charisma is important in astral space as it becomes
the rating for your astral body.

^WSee Also: ATTRIBUTES^n

